NOTICE

Google Tasks to Super Productivity Converter
=============================================

This project includes software developed by multiple contributors:


1. ORIGINAL PROJECT: GoogleTasksJSONtoTXT
   --------------------------------------
   Copyright (c) 2020 Thales
   Repository: https://github.com/thethales/GoogleTasksJSONtoTXT
   License: MIT

   The original project provided:
   - Google Tasks JSON parsing logic
   - TXT export functionality
   - GUI interface (run_gui.py)
   - CLI interface (run_silent.py)


2. SUPER PRODUCTIVITY CONVERTER ADDITIONS
   --------------------------------------
   Copyright (c) 2026 j57n-3co-x-5735
   License: MIT

   New functionality added:
   - Super Productivity JSON export (google_tasks_to_sp.py)
   - SP-compatible data structure generation
   - Subtask relationship preservation
   - Comprehensive unit tests (test_conversion.py)

   Developed with assistance from Claude (Anthropic).


3. THIRD-PARTY REFERENCES
   ----------------------

   Super Productivity
   ------------------
   This tool generates import files compatible with Super Productivity.
   Copyright (c) Johannes Millan and contributors
   Repository: https://github.com/johannesjo/super-productivity
   License: MIT

   The Super Productivity data format was derived by analyzing the
   publicly available source code. No Super Productivity code is
   included in this converter.

   Google Tasks / Google Takeout
   -----------------------------
   Google Tasks and Google Takeout are products of Google LLC.
   This tool processes the standard JSON export format.
   Google is a trademark of Google LLC.


